rows.name:
Mornin' everyone.
You're all looking better
rested than yesterday.

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Today is Fan-sama's state funeral,
correct?

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah, I think it was meant to be
happening in Seoris Plaza, right
outside the cathedral.

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0007
rows.name:
Seoris Plaza very not far away.
Let's go quickly!
